OL,3,CFoster mother of woman kept as slave
OL,4,Csays victim still 'terrified'
OL,6,FWords by Georgia Ziebart, Deputy
OL,7,FContent Editor
OL,9,FA vulnerable woman who was forced to
OL,10,Fwork as a house slave for 25 years is
OL,11,F"constantly living in fear", her
OL,12,Ffoster mother has told ITV News.
OL,14,FThe woman, who ITV News is calling K,
OL,15,Fwas 16 when she moved into the squalid
OL,16,Fhome of Amanda Wixon from Tewkesbury
OL,17,Fin 1995, and remained there until 2021.
OL,19,FWixon, aged 56, forced K to do manual
OL,20,Flabour, regularly assaulted her and
OL,21,Fdeprived her of food and healthcare.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773331878
OL,3,CFoster mother of woman kept as slave
OL,4,Csays victim still 'terrified'
OL,6,FK was finally freed in March 2021
OL,7,Fafter police went to the house in
OL,8,Fresponse to a report made by one of
OL,9,FWixon's sons.
OL,11,FOn Thursday, Wixon was sentenced to 13
OL,12,Fyears in jail.
OL,14,FShe had been found guilty of modern
OL,15,Fday slavery offences, including two
OL,16,Fcounts of requiring a person to
OL,17,Fperform forced or compulsory labour,
OL,18,Fone count of false imprisonment and
OL,19,Fthree counts of assault occasioning
OL,20,Factual bodily harm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
