PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773331878
OL,3,CFoster mother of woman kept as slave
OL,4,Csays victim still 'terrified'
OL,6,FK, who is now in her 40s, has learning
OL,7,Fdifficulties and now lives in the care
OL,8,Fof a foster family.
OL,10,FHer foster mother told ITV News that,
OL,11,Fwhen K first came to live with her,
OL,12,Fshe was "very shy, very anxious".
OL,14,F"She was underweight, they
OL,15,Fmalnourished her," she said, "She just
OL,16,Fwasn't looking good at all.
OL,18,F"It was really hard even giving her
OL,19,Fhugs; she didn't want me to hug her.
OL,20,FSo I used to say to her: 'When you're
OL,21,Fready, I'll be here for you'.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
