CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773331878
OL,3,CFoster mother of woman kept as slave
OL,4,Csays victim still 'terrified'
OL,6,F"And within a week she turned around
OL,7,Fand started being loving."
OL,9,F'She was terrified, petrified'
OL,11,FWixon's trial in January heard how K
OL,12,Fwas regularly beaten and also hit with
OL,13,Fa broom handle, knocking out her teeth.
OL,15,FWashing-up liquid would be squirted
OL,16,Fdown her throat, bleach splashed on
OL,17,Fher face, and she had her head
OL,18,Frepeatedly shaved against her will.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
