OL,3,CFoster mother of woman kept as slave
OL,4,Csays victim still 'terrified'
OL,6,F"Even now, she's got scars on her
OL,7,Fmouth," K's foster mother told ITV
OL,8,FNews.
OL,10,F"(Wixon) would lock her in her room,
OL,11,Fputting black bin bags over the window
OL,12,Fso she couldn't get any light.
OL,14,F"She would be dragged down the stairs.
OL,15,FI think she was locked in a cupboard.
OL,17,F"She wasn't allowed to wash. The only
OL,18,Ftime when she would get to wash was
OL,19,Fwhen (Wixon) was not there, or when
OL,20,Fshe'd sneak in to have a wash at
OL,21,Fnight."
