OL,3,CFoster mother of woman kept as slave
OL,4,Csays victim still 'terrified'
OL,6,FIn a voice note that K had made during
OL,7,Fher imprisonment, she is heard saying:
OL,8,F"I was in agony last night. I was
OL,9,Fcrying."
OL,11,F"(Wixon) said if I don't have nothing
OL,12,Fto do, she's going to f****** hit me
OL,13,Fmore.
OL,15,F"I wish I could go out, take (the dog)
OL,16,Ffor a walk. Wish I could do that, but
OL,17,FI can't."
OL,26,@sD@BpmsD@HpnwD@^pmwD@fpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
