OL,3,CFoster mother of woman kept as slave
OL,4,Csays victim still 'terrified'
OL,6,FThe foster mother said K is
OL,7,F"terrified" of Wixon, who was released
OL,8,Fon bail ahead of her sentencing. She
OL,9,Fdescribed an incident in which K
OL,10,F"bumped into" Wixon in a supermarket.
OL,12,F"(K) was hysterical. She was
OL,13,Fterrified, petrified. She's really
OL,14,Fscared of her.
OL,16,F"She was running around, it was
OL,17,Fhorrible. Going through the aisles and
OL,18,Fshe saw her, and that was it.
OL,26,@tD@BpmtD@Dpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773331878
OL,3,CFoster mother of woman kept as slave
OL,4,Csays victim still 'terrified'
OL,6,F"She hated it. She said they shouldn't
OL,7,Fallow her to walk around. I had to
OL,8,Fexplain to her, but it was really
OL,9,Fhard. She couldn't understand why they
OL,10,Flet her out.
OL,12,F"It's not fair. It's not fair at all."
OL,14,FQuestions for social services
OL,16,FK was 16 and still in college when she
OL,17,Fbegan living with Wixon. Her foster
OL,18,Fmother told ITV News the case raises
OL,19,Fquestions for social services.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
