OL,3,CFoster mother of woman kept as slave
OL,4,Csays victim still 'terrified'
OL,6,F"I personally think it's appalling,"
OL,7,Fshe said, "I don't know what happened,
OL,8,Fbut there needs to be a shake-up and I
OL,9,Fhope that nobody else goes through
OL,10,Fwhat she's been through.
OL,12,F"I think they need to be more alert
OL,13,Fand to help other people.
OL,15,F"It'd be a shame if other people go
OL,16,Fthrough what K has been through. It's
OL,17,Fbeen horrendous."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
