OL,3,CFoster mother of woman kept as slave
OL,4,Csays victim still 'terrified'
OL,6,FNeighbours of Wixon have previously
OL,7,Fsaid they'd contacted social services,
OL,8,Fbut nothing was done. One neighbour
OL,9,Fdescribed K as looking "like something
OL,10,Fout of a concentration camp".
OL,12,FGloucester Crown Court heard social
OL,13,Fservices were involved with the family
OL,14,Fin the late 1990s, but there were no
OL,15,Frecords of contact since.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
