OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773331878
OL,3,CFoster mother of woman kept as slave
OL,4,Csays victim still 'terrified'
OL,6,FOfficers described the woman's bedroom
OL,7,Fas looking like a "prison cell", with
OL,8,Fother bedrooms untidy and dirty. In
OL,9,Fpolice body-worn camera footage, an
OL,10,Fofficer can be heard remarking upon
OL,11,Fthe "filthy bedding" K was forced to
OL,12,Fsleep in.
OL,14,F"Other people went to the house as
OL,15,Fwell and they'd ask K if she was
OL,16,Falright and she'd say 'no'," K's
OL,17,Ffoster mother said.
OL,26,@oD@SOUoD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
