CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773331878
OL,3,CFoster mother of woman kept as slave
OL,4,Csays victim still 'terrified'
OL,6,F"She'd say 'no she's not', but nobody
OL,7,Fdid anything. That's what I don't
OL,8,Funderstand. They did nothing, they'd
OL,9,Fjust leave her there to suffer."
OL,11,F'Deep and lasting harm'
OL,13,FIn a letter written by K and read out
OL,14,Fby her foster mother ahead of Wixon's
OL,15,Fsentencing, she said she hopes the
OL,16,Fcourt "recognises the deep and lasting
OL,17,Fharm" of her abuse.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
