CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773331878
OL,3,CFoster mother of woman kept as slave
OL,4,Csays victim still 'terrified'
OL,6,FShe wrote: "For 25 years, I lived in
OL,7,Ffear, control and abuse. I was treated
OL,8,Fas though my life, my freedom and my
OL,9,Fvoice did not matter.
OL,11,F"Although my abuser has now been found
OL,12,Fguilty, the trauma and nightmares are
OL,13,Fsomething I still carry with me every
OL,14,Fday.
OL,16,F"I am now living with a wonderful
OL,17,Ffamily who show me kindness, patience
OL,18,Fand support. Their love is helping me
OL,19,Fslowly rebuild the life that was taken
OL,20,Ffrom me and begin to feel safe again.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773331878
OL,3,CFoster mother of woman kept as slave
OL,4,Csays victim still 'terrified'
OL,6,F"Nothing can give me back the 25 years
OL,7,FI lost, but I hope the court
OL,8,Frecognises the deep and lasting harm
OL,9,Fthis abuse has caused and delivers a
OL,10,Fsentence that truly reflects the
OL,11,Fseriousness of these crimes."
OL,13,FSpeaking ahead of the sentencing, K's
OL,14,Ffoster mother said she and K both feel
OL,15,FWixon "needs to pay" for her abuse.
OL,17,F"That's what she's hoping. That
OL,18,F(Wixon) will go down and pay for some
OL,19,Fof what she's done. She told me that
OL,20,Fshe'll feel safer if she knows she's
OL,21,Fput away.
OL,26,@zD@ApmzD@Gpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
