OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773331878
OL,3,CFoster mother of woman kept as slave
OL,4,Csays victim still 'terrified'
OL,6,F"If she doesn't, I don't think she'll
OL,7,Fever get closure from all of this."
OL,9,FK's foster mother told ITV News she
OL,10,Fwas now "enjoying her life" and has
OL,11,Fbeen on several holidays with her
OL,12,Ffoster family.
OL,14,F"She said she wants to go forward and
OL,15,Fthere are lots of things she wants to
OL,16,Fdo. She's enjoying life now, because
OL,17,FI'm trying to show her life what she
OL,18,Fdidn't have before."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
