SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773331878
OL,3,CFoster mother of woman kept as slave
OL,4,Csays victim still 'terrified'
OL,6,F"She's such a beautiful person. She's
OL,7,Fgot a lot of love to give. She's kind
OL,8,Fand warm, she's lovely."
OL,10,FA spokesperson for Gloucestershire
OL,11,FCounty Council said: "We would like to
OL,12,Fpraise the person at the centre of
OL,13,Fthis case for her bravery in reaching
OL,14,Fout for help. We first became aware of
OL,15,Fher tragic situation in 2021, at the
OL,16,Fstart of the police investigation.
OL,17,FSince then, the victim has been
OL,18,Fsupported by our Adult Social Care
OL,19,Fservices.
