OL,3,CFoster mother of woman kept as slave
OL,4,Csays victim still 'terrified'
OL,6,F"Now that this case has concluded, we
OL,7,Fwill be conducting a review to ensure
OL,8,Fthat all agencies do everything
OL,9,Fpossible to spot and prevent such
OL,10,Fabuse."
